						<div class="postbody">In a soundtrack you definitely want them in the order of the first time you hear the track in a "normal" playthrourgh.
<br />
<br />But since when sound effects are included in the soundtrack ?
<br />
<br />If by jingles you mean really short musics such as ones you get when getting an item, then they're usually like other music the first time you hear them. But if they're too much like sound effects then they're not included.</div>

					
