					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I always order them in numerical order. Looping tunes first, short tunes, sound effects and then D(PCM) voice samples.
<br />
<br />If they are not in order I arrange the looping songs together, short tunes, etc. It makes it simple and easy for me.</div>

					
